OL,3,CBoxer and part-time electrician Josh
OL,4,CPadley prepares for world title fight
OL,6,FBy Daniel Boal, ITV News Producer
OL,8,F"I'd just put my tea in the oven that
OL,9,Fnight and then we got the phone call
OL,10,Fthat every boxer dreams of."
OL,12,FOn Tuesday Josh Padley was working his
OL,13,Fday job, on the tools installing a
OL,14,Fsolar panel as an electrician in the
OL,15,Fnorth of England.
OL,17,FBut on Saturday, the 29-year-old will
OL,18,Ffight for the WBC lightweight title in
OL,19,FRiyadh, Saudi Arabia.
