OL,3,CBoxer and part-time electrician Josh
OL,4,CPadley prepares for world title fight
OL,6,FWorld champion Shakur Stevenson had
OL,7,Fbeen scheduled to face off against
OL,8,FAmerican Floyd Schofield.
OL,10,FBut, after Schofield fell ill, it will
OL,11,Fbe Yorkshire-born boxer/electrician
OL,12,FPadley who will take on the life-
OL,13,Fchanging fight.
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV News, Padley said: "It
OL,16,Fwas just a standard week really.
OL,17,FStandard Monday, Tuesday, I'd been to
OL,18,Fwork. I am a professional boxer, but I
OL,19,Falso have a day job.
