OL,3,CBoxer and part-time electrician Josh
OL,4,CPadley prepares for world title fight
OL,6,FStevenson, who has held multiple world
OL,7,Fchampionships in three weight classes,
OL,8,Fcomes into the fight with 22 wins and
OL,9,Fzero losses.
OL,11,FPadley will also come into the fight
OL,12,Fas an undefeated contender, coming off
OL,13,Fthe biggest win of his career after he
OL,14,Fbeat Mark Chamberlain at Wembley
OL,15,FStadium on the undercard of Anthony
OL,16,FJoshua vs Daniel Dubois in September
OL,17,F2024.
