OL,4,CPadley prepares for world title fight
OL,6,F"We've had an hour's training for a
OL,7,Fthree-weight world champion.
OL,9,F"When we landed yesterday, obviously
OL,10,Fwe got sorted out and then we went to
OL,11,Fthe gym for an hour for a little
OL,12,Fshakeout and hit a few pads.
OL,14,F"We watched a few clips on him and
OL,15,Fthat was my training for Shakur
OL,16,FStevenson, which is obviously crazy.
