OL,6,F"So if I go in there tomorrow and pull
OL,7,Fthis off, this is going to be one of
OL,8,Fthe crazy, greatest upset stories
OL,9,Fever. So that's my plan. That's what
OL,10,FI'm coming here to do."
OL,12,FThe Doncaster electrician will now
OL,13,Ftake centre ring to fight for a world
OL,14,Ftitle, on a card populated by elite
OL,15,Fchampions and some of the sport's
OL,16,Fbiggest names watching from ringside.
